thread.title: Nan

author: Nan
title: Nan
text:
I have purchased HP cartridges from Ink Farm for several years. Always prompt service and a quality product with an amazing low price compared to the options out there (Staples, Office Max, Office Depot).
Recently, the cartridges I ordered did not work in my printer. I called and within a few days I had replacements at no additional charge. I sent the defective ones back in a prepaid box so they could figure out what might have happened. I am very impressed with their caliber of service!
